txt.en: Ally to the Wardens of Annúminas
The Wardens of Annúminas consider you a stalwart ally and trusted confidant in all things that they do.
You must earn Ally standing with the Wardens of Annúminas
Your deeds on behalf of the Wardens of Annúminas have earned you a place alongside many of the other trusted allies they call upon in dire times.
